#: 2-0/key-features/ 2-1/key-features/
msgid ""
"Location tracking helps you find your device if you lose it. Remote wipe and"
" lock capabilities help you keep your personal information safe."
msgstr ""
"Mai binciko wurin zama na taimaka maka ka nemo na'urarka idan ka rasata. "
"Masu sharewa daga nesa da abubuwa masu yiwuwa na rufewa na taimaka maka "
"ajiye bayanai na ƙashin kanka lafiya."

#: 2-0/introduction/ 2-1/introduction/
msgid ""
"Use your phone in your language, control your data usage and personalize it "
"by creating your own ringtones. You can also download locally-relevant apps "
"that enrich and simplify your daily life. Firefox OS is truly a phone made "
"with you in mind."
msgstr ""
"Yi amfani da wayarka a yarenka, sarrafa yadda ka yi amfani da bayananka kuma"
" ka mayar da su na ka ta hanyar ƙirƙirar kiɗan kira naka. Kuma za ka iya "
"sauke aikace-aikace da suka dace waɗanda za su inganta kuma su sauƙaƙa "
"rayuwarka ta yau da kullum. Firefox OS haƙiƙa waya ce da aka yi sabo da kai "
"a zuci."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid "Remotely wipe the device."
msgstr "Share na'urar daga nesa."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"With the Firefox Marketplace, the best preloaded apps and an awesome user "
"experience, Firefox OS is packed with the features that users are looking "
"for in a smartphone."
msgstr ""
"Tare da Wurin Kasuwanci na Firefox, mafi kyan aikace-aikace da aka loda kuma"
" mai ingancin koyo na mai amfani, Firefox OS an cikata da siffofi da mai "
"amfani ke nema a babbar wayar hannu."

#: 2-0/key-features/ 2-1/key-features/
msgid "Ringtones"
msgstr "Kaɗe-kaɗen kira"

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid "Remotely lock the device."
msgstr "Kulle na'ura daga nesa."

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid "Create your own ringtones"
msgstr "Ƙirƙiri kiɗan kira na ka"

#: 2-0/key-features/ 2-1/key-features/
msgid "Find My Device"
msgstr "Nemo Na'urata"

#: 2-0/take-the-challenge/ 2-1/take-the-challenge/
msgid ""
"Since it’s made by Firefox, Firefox OS is backed by a global community "
"working on your behalf and with your interests in mind."
msgstr ""
"Tunda Firefox ne suka yi, Firefox OS na da goyon bayan al'ummar duniya masu "
"aiki a madadinka da kuma saka bukatarka a zuci."

#: 2-0/demo-tips/ 2-1/demo-tips/
msgid "Rich media experience"
msgstr "Kyakkyawan koyo na kaɗe-kaɗe"

#: 2-0/key-features/ 2-1/key-features/
msgid ""
"Customize your Firefox OS phone by creating new ringtones from your music "
"collection or from songs you download from the Web."
msgstr ""
"Tsara wayarka ta Firefox OS ta ƙirƙirar sababbin kaɗe-kaɗen kira daga "
"waƙoƙin da ka tara ko daga waƙe-waƙen da ka sauke daga Yanar gizo."
